tafsir[24]{c,v,t}:
  37,103,"Nde ɓe jebbilaninoo yamiroore Alla nden, Ibraahiima hippiri geɗal makko, tiinde nden, fii hirsugol mo."
  37,104,"Men noddi Ibraahiima fewndo o hittiniraynoo waɗugol yamiroore Alla nden, ka hirsugol geɗaljo makko on, wiide: ko an yo Ibraahiima!"
  37,105,"Pellet, a laatinirii koyɗol maa ngol, fiɓugol hirsude geɗaljo maa on. Awa ko wano Men yoɓitirt maa non firtingol ma nden huunde saɗtunde, woni ko Men yoɓitirta moƴƴinooɓe ɓen; Men ɓoora ɓe e kulaleeji e saɗteendeeji."
  37,106,"Pellet, ko ɗum ɗoo woni jarrabuyee ɓannguɗo on. Ibraahiima hawrii e mun."
  37,107,"Men soktiri Ismaa'iila, dammol mawnungol, ko hirsee, hara wanaa kanko."
  37,108,"Men accani Ibraahiima, mantoore labaande, e mofte sakkitiiɗe ɗen."
  37,109,"Alla hiwrike mo, O du'anike mo kadi kisal e kala lorra."
  37,110,"Ko wano Men yoɓitiri Ibraahiima e ɗoftaare makko nden, Men yoɓitirta moƴƴinooɓe ɓen."
  37,111,"Kanko Ibraahiima, ko o jeyanooɗo e jeyaaɓe Amen gomɗimɓe, hunnuɓe sifaaji jeyeede Alla."
  37,112,"Men wewlintiniri mo geɗaljo goo, wonoowo Annabaajo, e jeyaaɗo moƴƴo; on woni Ishaaqa. Ɗum ko njoɓdi ɗoftagol mo Alla ngol, ka hirsugol Ismaa'iila, ɓiɗɗo makko bajjo on nun."
  37,113,"Men jippini barki e makko, e dow geɗal makko Ishaaqa. Men ɗuɗɗinani ɓe neema; wano ɗuuɗireede ɓiɗɓe. Hino e geyngol maɓɓe ngol non, moƴƴinɗo ɗoftagpl Joomi mun, e tooñirɗo hoore-mun yeddugol faggitoo ɓanngina bone."
  37,114,"Gomɗii Men moƴƴorike e dow Muusaa, e nene gooto makko on Haaruuna, Annabaaku ngun."
  37,115,"Men daɗndi ɓe, kamɓe e yimɓe maɓɓe ɓiɗɓe Israa'iila ɓen, maccinireede Fir'awna, e yoolagol."
  37,116,"Men walli ɓe e Fir'awna e konu mun, ɓe fooli ayɓe maɓɓe ɓen."
  37,117,"Men okki Muusaa e neene gooto makko on Haaruuna, Deftere Tawreeta nden, immorde ka Alla, ɓanngunde, nde jilɓuya alah e mayre."
  37,118,"Men fewniri ɓe, e laawol focciingol ngol. Ngol woni laawol diina lislaamu kan, ɗowirayngol e welayee seniiɗo taguɗo On."
  37,119,"Men accani ɓe mantoore e jantoore labaande, e mofte sakkitiiɓe ɓen."
  37,120,"Alla hiwrorike ɓe hiwraandu teddundu, O mantii ɓe, O du'oranike ɓe hisugol e kala bone."
  37,121,"Ko wano Men yoɓitiri non Muusaa e Haaruuna, woni ko Men yoɓitirta moƴƴinooɓe ɗfotagol Joomi mun ɓen."
  37,122,"Muusaa e Haaruuna, ko jeyanooɓe e jeyaaɓe Amen gomɗimɓe Alla, golliri sari'a Makko on."
  37,123,"Pellet, Ilyaasa kadi, ko jeyanooɗo e Nulaaɓe Alla ɓen. Alla moƴƴorino e makko Annabaaku e Nulal."
  37,124,"Janto nde o maakannoo yimɓe mako ɓen o nulaa e mun ɓen, ka ɓiɗɓe Israa'iila: Ko onon yo yimɓe am, e on hulirtaa Alla ɗoftagol yamirooje Makko ɗen, wano wootinɗingol Mo, e woɗɗitagol haɗaaɗi Makko ɗin, wano sirku?"
  37,125,"E on reway sanamuuru mon wi'eteende "Ba'ala" ndun, accon ɗon Alla, ɓurɗo moƴƴude tagu On?"
  37,126,"Ko Alla woni Joomi mon, woni taguɗo on, O tagi baabiraaɓe mon ɓen ado ɗum. Ko On hanndi e reweede, wanaa goɗɗum goo, wano sanamuuji mon, ɗi duncataa ɗi lorrataa."